msgctxt "an8.12:19.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, sīha, pariyāyo, yena maṃ pariyāyena sammā vadamāno vadeyya: "
msgstr "In this sense you could rightly say that I teach annihilationism. "

msgctxt "an8.12:19.6"
msgid "‘ucchedavādo samaṇo gotamo, ucchedāya dhammaṃ deseti, tena ca sāvake vinetī’ti. (3) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc20
msgctxt "an8.12:20.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, sīha, pariyāyo, yena maṃ pariyāyena sammā vadamāno vadeyya: "
msgstr "And what’s the sense in which you could rightly say that "

msgctxt "an8.12:20.2"
msgid "‘jegucchī samaṇo gotamo, jegucchitāya dhammaṃ deseti, tena ca sāvake vinetī’ti? "
