msgid "jigucchāmi anekavihitānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ samāpattiyā. "
msgstr "and by attainment of the many kinds of unskillful things. "

msgctxt "an8.12:20.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, sīha, pariyāyo, yena maṃ pariyāyena sammā vadamāno vadeyya: "
